import Noidung from '../tintuc/noidung';
import Tieude from '../tintuc/tieude';

function Xuhuong() {
    return ( <
        div className = "news_xh" >
        <
        div className = "news_td" >
        <
        div className = "td_title" >
        <
        i className = "fas fa-chart-line fa-2x"
        style = {
            { color: 'blue' } }
        /> <
        Tieude / >
        <
        /div>

        <
        div className = "td_tag" >
        <
        div className = "tag" >
        <
        a href > Học sinh < /a> <
        /div> <
        div className = "tag" >
        <
        a href > Học sinh < /a> <
        /div> <
        div className = "tag" >
        <
        a href > Học sinh < /a> <
        /div> <
        /div> <
        /div> <
        div className = "news_nd" >
        <
        Noidung / >
        <
        Noidung / >
        <
        Noidung / >
        <
        /div> <
        /div>
    );
}
export default Xuhuong;
